AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ This module is used everywhere 2 redundant detections are needed on working area to avoid activation with safety shoes. If the alarm is enable, one alarm shall be generated when detection 1 is true and some time later the detection 2 is still false or when detection 2 is true and some time later the detection 1 is still false then Alarm is generated. Alarm is disable from HMI, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level and do action in the Alarm summary. When the conditions to generate the alarm is disappear, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. The alarm is reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal. ================================================================================
